PR created: [jdx/mise#10699](https://github.com/jdx/mise/pull/10699)

Fixed monorepo task metadata rendering so `sources`/`outputs` templates can see `[env]` from the task’s own config hierarchy. Added e2e coverage for completion plus running the task from the monorepo root.

Verified with `cargo fmt --check`, `cargo check -q`, and `mise run test:e2e e2e/tasks/test_task_ls_complete_monorepo`.

Note: the pre-existing unrelated `.github/workflows/*` edits are still unstaged in the worktree.

